      • oneResult

        public final List<Object> oneResult()
        Description copied from interface: PrologQuery
        Return the equivalent Java objects that conform the solution set for the current query. The solution set is a Java objects list and every term is a conversion of the instance value for the variables not anonymous involved in the query.
